title: San Francisco Treat
description: Fellas discuss the stunning results of a San Francisco school board recall and what it means for the coming red wave before laughing about alcohol on airplanes and dinosaur theft. Sen. Ron Johnson from Wisconsin and Trent England from Save Our States both join the progrum for interviews.
